name: "Future Wanderer"
description:
In a few years many areas on earth will be uninhabited due to natural disasters that will occur.
The wanderer in his attempt to find a habitable place on the planet discovers a beautiful landscape full with  dandelion hills and a forgotten piano, excited for his discovery ,he begins to play some piano melodies remembering the good old days with the help of music, giving him optimism for a better future on earth, a planet that was destroyed by humanity.

music made by my dear friend @fantonbeat
